  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aa377238-cc72-43b7-a9a3-bc78c8097b03\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0090f2ab-bcaa-4bd7-8ded-d45d8bb27d40\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-46e6767e-82c3-48a9-a775-488dd98bc9d8\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 15</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-51b4a8e2-b016-4a5b-98df-8b2e3172d4b6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6dc820e5-f7a7-4225-a27b-dc9acc1b081d\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b30549af-c6d4-4f03-aa3a-06932ad4047c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f218dbd4-81b5-4446-bab0-bd135156d845\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[요소정리]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c6c3ba32-6c8a-4b6d-9ae7-6b4e0696aacb\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-46348bb8-3bb2-4cb4-8c8d-6fe781f5464f\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>앞으로 7일간은 주문에 필요한 인쇄의 기본적인 요소를 정리하는 시간을 갖도록 하겠습니다. 27년의 인쇄 노하우를 가진 제가 좋은 자료를 만들기 위해 본격적으로 정리한 것이니 잘 읽어보시고 인쇄 주문이나 발주시 참고하셨으면 합니다. 인쇄에서 기본이 되는 범위에 대한 설명입니다. 시작합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ebcc8958-c141-4d16-bc93-fee2e1711794\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1f68e194-761b-44c5-9c92-5d19cf396641\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-a6ccb9da-1a7e-4c7c-9078-7694996dc4ee\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7c12c701-be00-4ac1-a334-e6fd710d7eba\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-806961d9-0a6b-4797-934a-bfc4c5de93a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>페이지란?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9dab86e0-86d2-47d2-9469-306b7971bccd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d9120a2d-18ba-449d-8455-2601dbf94e9e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs30 se-ff-system se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f1e20954-b34d-4434-ad55-fbdf055cebe2\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>페이지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff-system se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b2c4ea31-909d-4ad2-801d-3ec5c64b34c7\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3ffc902f-8b08-4c0a-8a20-b6cd717af4c9\" style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\">page</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a26c5db4-573c-4d4b-88f9-a64ed6e3a8e2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-cente